## Technical Specifications (Phase 1)

### 1. Schema Definitions (`src/types/schema.ts`)
```typescript
export interface VideoProject {
  version: string;
  metadata: {
    title: string;
    width: number;
    height: number;
    fps: number;
    totalDurationSec: number;
  };
  theme: {
    stylePreset: "Apple" | "Stripe" | "Linear" | "Notion" | "ModernSaaS" | "Enterprise" | "Futuristic";
    colors: {
      background: string;
      surface: string;
      primary: string;
      secondary: string;
      text: string;
      mutedText: string;
      accent: string;
      border: string;
      charts: string[];
    };
    typography: {
      headingFont: string;
      bodyFont: string;
      monoFont: string;
    };
    glassmorphism: boolean;
    borderRadius: number;
  };
  scenes: Scene[];
  audio?: {
    musicUrl?: string;
    musicVolume?: number;
  };
}

export interface Scene {
  id: string;
  type: "TitleReveal" | "KineticText" | "DashboardShowcase" | "CTASection";
  durationFrames: number;
  transitionIn?: {
    type: "fade" | "slide-up" | "slide-left" | "zoom" | "none";
    durationFrames: number;
  };
  props: Record<string, any>;
  overlays?: OverlayLayer[];
}

export interface OverlayLayer {
  id: string;
  type: "text" | "cursor" | "badge" | "arrow" | "zoom-focus";
  startTimeFrame: number;
  durationFrames: number;
  position: { x: number; y: number; width?: number; height?: number };
  animation: {
    type: "pop" | "fade" | "draw-path" | "float";
    durationFrames: number;
  };
  props: Record<string, any>;
}
```

### 2. Animation Foundation
- **Spring Presets (`animation/springs.ts`)**:
  - `snappy`: damping 20, stiffness 160, mass 0.5 (fast popups, menus, clicks)
  - `smooth`: damping 26, stiffness 120, mass 0.8 (large slide-ins, device layout entries)
  - `slow`: damping 40, stiffness 80, mass 1.0 (heavy text reveals, background pans)
- **Easings (`animation/easings.ts`)**:
  - Standard ease-out-quart: `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)`
  - Standard ease-in-out: `cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1)`

### 3. Core Primitives (`components/primitives/`)
- **AnimatedText**: Splitting sentences into words/characters, using spring delay to mask translate-up.
- **GradientBackground**: Fluid CSS animation or canvas animating multiple radial/linear gradients.
- **GlassPanel**: backdrop-filter blur (12px), border (1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08)), box-shadow.
- **BrowserChrome**: Mock window layout, traffic-light actions, web address bar, clean shadows.
- **NoiseTexture**: absolute overlay SVG/CSS noise pattern with low opacity (0.02 - 0.04).

### 4. Components & Compositions
- **TitleReveal**: Reveal high-contrast tagline and headline sequentially.
- **KineticText**: Kinetic text engine breaking paragraphs into distinct kinetic sizes/weights.
- **DashboardShowcase**: Browser window wrapping a mockup image, with floating cursor moving and clicking on specific hotspots.
- **CTASection**: Dynamic glass card containing headers, pricing highlights, and animated button pulses.
- **VideoProject**: Sequencer using `<Series>` and mapping scene configurations.

### 5. Validation Layers (`validation/`)
- **validateSchema**: Compiles `scene-graph.schema.json` via Ajv to guarantee strict properties.
- **validateSceneGraph**:
  - Sum of scene durations == `fps * totalDurationSec`.
  - Scenes duration must be positive.
  - Image URLs must be verified if a DashboardShowcase is chosen.

